channel.title: I have problem with porting
channel.description:
Open your cmd by going to Start > Run > cmd. Type in `ipconfig´ It will say your default gateway, so type that in your browser and you will get a login screen. Skip the username part and fill in `admin´ at the password field. Click the Applications & Gaming tab and fill in the things. Start & End = 43594 Proctol = Both IP Address = Your IP And make sure you enable it! with this!
